Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:01:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(890,576.647)}{\fad(2600,2300)}《约伯记》38章4,7节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}弟弟\N{\rEn}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}母亲\N{\rEn}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}是他们领我来到你门前\N{\rEn}It was they who led me to your door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}修女教导我们  生命之路有两条\N{\rEn}The nuns taught us there were two ways through life —
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}或是选择自然之道 顺应天性\N{\rEn}the way of nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}或是接受主的恩典 追随指引\N{\rEn}and the way of grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你必须选择你自己的道路\N{\rEn}You have to choose which one you'll follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}选择跟从主的指引就无法事事顺心\N{\rEn}Grace doesn't try to please itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}承受被轻视 被遗忘 被厌弃\N{\rEn}Accepts being slighted, forgotten, disliked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}被侮辱与被伤害\N{\rEn}Accepts insults and injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}选择顺应天性 取悦自己\N{\rEn}Nature only wants to please itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}感谢主赐予我们食物..\N{\rEn}Bless, O Lord, this food —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}也取悦他人\N{\rEn}Get others to please it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}感谢你的爱与恩宠..\N{\rEn}Your loving and faithful service —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}自然之道想要主宰万物\N{\rEn}Likes to lord it over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}保佑这些孩子\N{\rEn}Bless these boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}..让万物顺应天性\N{\rEn}To have its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}生命中总有苦痛\N{\rEn}It finds reasons to be unhappy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但同时 世界又是如此灿烂\N{\rEn}when all the world is shining around it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}爱在天地间徜徉\N{\rEn}and love is smiling through all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}她们说 追随主的指引的人\N{\rEn}They taught us that no one who loves the way of grace
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不会有悲惨的结局\N{\rEn}ever comes to a bad end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我将永远对你虔诚\N{\rEn}I will be true to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不论发生什么\N{\rEn}whatever comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}哦 天啊！\N{\rEn}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的儿子\N{\rEn}My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我只想去死\N{\rEn}I just wanna die,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}去陪他\N{\rEn}to be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}上帝把他接走了\N{\rEn}He's in God's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}上帝从未离开过他\N{\rEn}He was in God's hands the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不是吗？\N{\rEn}Wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的希望\N{\rEn}My hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的上帝\N{\rEn}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.99,注释,,0,0,0,,*出自《圣经·旧约》诗篇23:4*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不再畏惧恶的存在\N{\rEn}“I shall fear no evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不再畏惧了 因为你与我同在\N{\rEn}Fear no evil, for you are with me.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你又能得到什么？\N{\rEn}What did you gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.57,注释,,0,0,0,,*出自《圣经·旧约》诗篇22:11*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}请不要远离我 因为劫难临近了\N{\rEn}“Be not far from me, for trouble is near.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}走吧 我们没事儿了\N{\rEn}Go on now. We're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们没事儿了\N{\rEn}We're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}谢谢你 谢谢\N{\rEn}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你还惦记着他\N{\rEn}You have your memories of him and, uh —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但你得学着坚强\N{\rEn}You have to be strong now and —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}听我说 痛苦..\N{\rEn}I know, uh, the pain will —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}痛苦会过去的\N{\rEn}It will pass in time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这也许并不容易\N{\rEn}It might seem... hard, my saying that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但的确是这样\N{\rEn}but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}可我不想忘记\N{\rEn}I don't want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}生活总要继续\N{\rEn}Life goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}人总有一死\N{\rEn}People pass along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}没有什么是永恒不变的\N{\rEn}Nothing stays the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你还有两个孩子\N{\rEn}You still got the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}主给予 他也收回\N{\rEn}- The Lord gives, and the Lord takes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他就是这样\N{\rEn}That's the way he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他放任那些\N{\rEn}He sends flies to wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}本该由他治愈的伤口于不顾\N{\rEn}that he should heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我还没来得及告诉他 我有多对不起他\N{\rEn}I never got a chance to tell him how sorry I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}有天晚上\N{\rEn}One night he...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他无缘无故的朝自己脸上\N{\rEn}punched him — himself in the face
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}打了一拳\N{\rEn}for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那时我在弹琴 他就坐在我的旁边 我批评了他给我翻谱的方式\N{\rEn}He was sittin' next to me at the piano, and I criticized the way he'd turned the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我让他感到很自责\N{\rEn}I made him feel shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我感到很羞愧\N{\rEn}My shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}可怜的孩子\N{\rEn}That poor boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}可怜的孩子\N{\rEn}That poor boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你如何来到我的身边\N{\rEn}How did you come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}以何种面目\N{\rEn}In what shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}何种伪装\N{\rEn}What disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我看到了我小时候\N{\rEn}I see the child I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}看到了我的弟弟\N{\rEn}I see my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}纯真\N{\rEn}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}善良\N{\rEn}Kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他十九岁时就死了\N{\rEn}He died when he was 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}查查看 这里有问题\N{\rEn}Just check this — this one against this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}她想复合\N{\rEn}She wants to get back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但这段故事已经翻篇了 该说的也都说了\N{\rEn}Chapter's closed. Story's been told.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你打算怎么办\N{\rEn}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}看着办吧\N{\rEn}Experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}嗯 都是关于你的前途\N{\rEn}Yeah, it's all about your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你还不懂\N{\rEn}You don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我觉得自己四处碰壁\N{\rEn}I just feel like I'm bumping into walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不知道怎样才算公平\N{\rEn}I don't know how to be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}世风堕落\N{\rEn}The world is gone to the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}人们变得贪得无厌 道德沦丧\N{\rEn}People are greedy. They keep getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}过些年\N{\rEn}Years later —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们想让你也变成这样的人\N{\rEn}They try to get you into their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}会陷入同样的困境\N{\rEn}Drifting back into the same swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}爸 我不该说那些话\N{\rEn}Hey, Dad, I'm sorry I said what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}嗯 我每天都会想起他\N{\rEn}Yeah. Yeah. I think about him every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不该说那些 对不起\N{\rEn}I just shouldn't have said what I did, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不 只是 这个时代..\N{\rEn}No, it's just, oh... this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你在想什么 {\rzh}-我明白你已经尽力了 \N{\rEn}{\rEn}- What are you thinking?  \N- I know you did everything you could.\N{\rEn}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}其中只有两条被顾客驳回了\N{\rEn}And only two of those were turned down by the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我是如何失去了你？\N{\rEn}How did I lose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}四处徘徊\N{\rEn}Wandered?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}忘记了你\N{\rEn}Forgot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}回想起\N{\rEn}Remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}噢 你别闹\N{\rEn}Oh, no, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}看 你明明挺开心的\N{\rEn}See? There, you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}至少有点儿吧\N{\rEn}Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}好吧\N{\rEn}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}所以 我们仅仅能收回成本\N{\rEn}So... we barely broke even.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来找我\N{\rEn}Find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}她是怎么熬过来的\N{\rEn}How did she bear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.86,0:23:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}母亲\N{\rEn}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我对你不够虔诚么\N{\rEn}Was I false to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.03,0:24:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}主啊\N{\rEn}Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.12,0:25:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}为什么\N{\rEn}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.38,0:25:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你那时在哪里呢\N{\rEn}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.94,0:26:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你知道吗\N{\rEn}Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.96,0:26:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}对你来说我们算什么呢\N{\rEn}Who are we to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.65,0:26:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}回答我吧\N{\rEn}Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.57,0:31:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们祈求你的回应\N{\rEn}We cry to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.29,0:31:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的灵魂\N{\rEn}My soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.67,0:31:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的儿子\N{\rEn}My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.85,0:31:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}倾听我们\N{\rEn}Hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.79,0:39:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的生命之光啊\N{\rEn}Light of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.42,0:39:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我追寻着你\N{\rEn}I search for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.18,0:39:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的希望\N{\rEn}My hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.07,0:40:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的孩子\N{\rEn}My child.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.69,0:41:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}是你让她领我来到你门前\N{\rEn}You spoke to me through her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.74,0:41:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你在天上与我交流\N{\rEn}You spoke with me from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.24,0:41:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那些树\N{\rEn}The trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.87,0:41:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}在我意识到我爱你\N{\rEn}Before I knew I loved you,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.96,0:41:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}相信你之前\N{\rEn}believed in you.
