Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.34,1:07:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不幸也会降临在好人身上\N{\rEn}Misfortune befalls the good as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.05,1:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们无法避免不幸的降临\N{\rEn}We can't protect ourselves against it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.22,1:07:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}也无法庇护我们的孩子\N{\rEn}We can't protect our children.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.77,1:07:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们不能对自己说 尽管我们并不开心\N{\rEn}We can't say to ourselves, even if I'm not happy,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.73,1:07:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}却能保证孩子们开心\N{\rEn}I'm going to make sure they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.57,1:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们现在生活得顺风顺水\N{\rEn}We run before the wind.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.48,1:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}就认为他会永远保护我们\N{\rEn}We think that it will carry us forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.49,1:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}并不是这样\N{\rEn}It will not.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.03,1:08:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们如云般消散\N{\rEn}We vanish as a cloud.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.07,1:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}如秋日的草般枯萎\N{\rEn}We wither as the autumn grass
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.28,1:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}如树被连根拔起\N{\rEn}and, like a tree, are rooted up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.79,1:08:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那么 是宇宙秩序出错了吗\N{\rEn}Is there some fraud in the scheme of the universe?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.13,1:08:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}没有什么是不朽的\N{\rEn}Is there nothing which is deathless,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.50,1:08:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}没有什么是不灭的\N{\rEn}nothing which does not pass away?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.59,1:08:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们不能停滞不前\N{\rEn}We cannot stay where we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.93,1:08:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们必须继续前行\N{\rEn}We must journey forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.31,1:08:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们必须找到那个比财富与命运更重要的东西\N{\rEn}We must find that which is greater than fortune or fate.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.73,1:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}除此之外 没有什么能够带给我们安宁\N{\rEn}Nothing can bring us peace but that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.90,1:08:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}智慧公正的人难道可以\N{\rEn}Is the body of the wise man or the just
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.15,1:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}免受肉体疼痛\N{\rEn}exempt from any pain,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.36,1:08:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}焦虑不安\N{\rEn}from any disquietude,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.36,1:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}容颜折损\N{\rEn}from the deformity that might blight its beauty,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.20,1:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}健康不再的折磨吗\N{\rEn}from the weakness that might destroy its health?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.58,1:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你相信上帝吗\N{\rEn}Do you trust in God?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.58,1:08:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}约伯相信 他曾经离上帝很近\N{\rEn}Job, too, was close to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.38,1:09:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那么你的朋友 孩子 你的安全就得到保障了吗\N{\rEn}Are your friends and children your security?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.72,1:09:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这世上没有可以逃离劫难的庇护之所\N{\rEn}There is no hiding place in all the world where trouble may not find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.26,1:09:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}没有人知道什么时候 悲痛会袭来\N{\rEn}No one knows when sorrow might visit his house
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.27,1:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}就像约伯一样\N{\rEn}any more than Job did.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.23,1:09:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}约伯失去一切的那瞬间\N{\rEn}The very moment everything was taken away from Job,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.56,1:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他明白是上帝拿走了这一切\N{\rEn}he knew it was the Lord who'd taken it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.99,1:09:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他背弃了他的过去\N{\rEn}He turned from the passing shows of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.07,1:09:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那段试图追寻永恒的过去\N{\rEn}He sought that which is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.70,1:09:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}难道他只看到上帝之手意味着给予\N{\rEn}Does he alone see God's hand who sees that he gives?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.37,1:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}却没有看到上帝之手\N{\rEn}Or does not also the one see God's hand —
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.96,1:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你就是你要找的人 -同时也意味着收回\N{\rEn}- I'm your man. - who sees that he takes away?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.84,1:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}难道他只看到上帝将面孔转向他\N{\rEn}Or does he alone see God who sees God turn his face towards him?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.51,1:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}却不知道同时也是上帝在转向背对他的方向\N{\rEn}Does not also he see God who sees God turn his back?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.93,1:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那是我的一个朋友 他名下有镇子的半数房产\N{\rEn}That's a friend of mine. He owns half the real estate in town.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.23,1:09:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}Frank Johnson\N{\rEn}Frank Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.06,1:09:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他做理发师起家\N{\rEn}Started out as a barber.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.03,1:10:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但他成就了番大事业\N{\rEn}But he built something big.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.78,1:10:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}现在你可能会认为他是圣三位一体中的第四人\N{\rEn}Now you'd think he was the fourth person of the Holy Trinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.04,1:10:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们对自己的财富闭口不谈\N{\rEn}They never talk about their money.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.42,1:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}挨饿的都是不该挨饿的人\N{\rEn}Wrong people go hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.17,1:10:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}死去的都是不该死的人\N{\rEn}Die.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.72,1:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}被爱的都是不值得被爱的人\N{\rEn}Wrong people get loved.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.51,1:10:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这个世界充满尔虞我诈\N{\rEn}- The world lives by trickery.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.22,1:10:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}如果你想要成功 你就不能太过善良\N{\rEn}If you want to succeed, you can't be too good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.90,1:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}嗨 小伙子们 你们今天过得怎么样呀\N{\rEn}Hey there, young fellas. How y'all doin' today?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.99,1:10:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你们想不想吃烧烤\N{\rEn}Do all y'all want some barbecue?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.03,1:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}一磅牛胸肉怎么卖\N{\rEn}How 'bout a pound of brisket?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.61,1:11:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}对不起\N{\rEn}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.78,1:11:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我能用绳索套你吗\N{\rEn}Can I rope you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.20,1:11:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}如果你想的话\N{\rEn}If you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.26,1:11:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不错呀\N{\rEn}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.13,1:11:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你抓到我了\N{\rEn}Caught me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.72,1:11:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这叫什么\N{\rEn}What's that called?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.56,1:11:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这是个蝴蝶绳结\N{\rEn}This is a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.14,1:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}为什么叫这个名字\N{\rEn}Why do they call it that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.56,1:12:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}因为它可以飘动起来\N{\rEn}'Cause it floats.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.42,1:12:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你打算就这么无所事事地坐着抠肚脐么\N{\rEn}You just gonna sit around, picking lint out of your navel?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.30,1:12:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你以后要出人头地 -张嘴 让我看看\N{\rEn}- You 're gonna have a record. - Open. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.67,1:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你的成就会伴随你一生\N{\rEn}And it's gonna follow you around for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.26,1:12:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}如果你搞砸了 你可能连政审都无法通过\N{\rEn}If you mess up, you might not be able to get a security clearance.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.77,1:12:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}人们会很好奇\N{\rEn}People will ask why.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.73,1:12:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们会指责我的教育\N{\rEn}They'll point the finger at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.48,1:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}而一切都取决于你\N{\rEn}All but you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.74,1:12:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的儿子啊\N{\rEn}My son.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.32,1:13:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你都除干净了吗\N{\rEn}Did you get it all?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.19,1:13:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}是的 先生\N{\rEn}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.06,1:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}像这样站着 明白吗 来吧\N{\rEn}Stand like this. Right? Okay? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.56,1:14:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你要表现出你很害怕 不想打架 不想惹麻烦\N{\rEn}You act like you're scared, you're in trouble. You don't wanna fight, you don't want trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.94,1:14:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}然后一看到对方眨眼 你就痛扁他 明白吗\N{\rEn}The minute you see him blink, crack him. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.74,1:14:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}明白吗 来吧 第三回合了\N{\rEn}- Okay? Come on. Three-quarters.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.20,1:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}防守 你在防守 对吧\N{\rEn}Cover. You're gonna cover, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.78,1:14:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来打我 来啊\N{\rEn}Okay, hit. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.33,1:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不错 再用力点 不错 右手打得不错 换左手试试\N{\rEn}Nice. Nice. Harder. Nice. That's a good right. Let's see your left.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.58,1:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这是最重要的 懂么\N{\rEn}It's the most important thing. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.58,1:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你这只手出拳 另只手得这么保护自己\N{\rEn}You come in this way, you put your guard up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.58,1:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来打我 来啊 打我\N{\rEn}Hit me. Come on. Hit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.17,1:14:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来啊 Jack 来打我\N{\rEn}Come on! Come on, Jack, hit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.46,1:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}打我啊 打我啊 来啊来啊\N{\rEn}Hit me. Hit me. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.88,1:14:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来打这里 来啊 儿子\N{\rEn}Here it is. Here it is. Hit it. Come on, Son! Come on, Son.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.13,1:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}让你出左拳 你在干啥呢\N{\rEn}Left — What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.27,1:14:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}把自己拍拍干净\N{\rEn}Brush yourself off.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.64,1:14:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}左手 别把舌头露出来 会被人打断的\N{\rEn}Left. Don't leave your tongue out. You're gonna lose it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.81,1:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}左手 左手\N{\rEn}Left. Left.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.90,1:14:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}右手 右手\N{\rEn}Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.78,1:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}左手 用力点\N{\rEn}Left. Harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.57,1:14:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}用力 用力\N{\rEn}Harder. Harder!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.24,1:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来啊 打我 来打我\N{\rEn}Come on, hit me. Hit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.49,1:15:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来啊儿子 来打我\N{\rEn}Come on, Son, hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.53,1:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}给我点颜色看看 让我看看你都学到了什么\N{\rEn}Give me somethin'. Show me what you got.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.75,1:15:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来啊 好吧算了\N{\rEn}Come on. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.50,1:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你准备好了吗\N{\rEn}- You ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.09,1:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}好好吃饭\N{\rEn}One meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.16,1:15:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}哈\N{\rEn}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.17,1:15:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}滚\N{\rEn}Leave the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.05,1:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你也想滚吗\N{\rEn}You too?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.31,1:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你打算继续违抗我吗 -没有 先生\N{\rEn}- You gonna continue to defy me? - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.31,1:16:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你打断我了\N{\rEn}You interrupted me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.14,1:16:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我还没说完\N{\rEn}I wasn't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.40,1:16:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我说完了吗\N{\rEn}Am I finished?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.23,1:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}没有吗\N{\rEn}No?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.86,1:16:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-没有 -那我真是谢谢你了 殿下\N{\rEn}- No. - Thank you, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.67,1:17:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}编造故事\N{\rEn}Makes up stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.84,1:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}乱定规矩\N{\rEn}Original words.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.10,1:17:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他说不要把胳膊架在桌子上\N{\rEn}He says don't put your elbows on the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.19,1:17:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你们准备好了吗\N{\rEn}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.06,1:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他自己却这么做\N{\rEn}He does.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.49,1:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}辱骂别人\N{\rEn}Insults people.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.87,1:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不懂得关心\N{\rEn}Doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.66,1:17:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我还记得你出生的时候\N{\rEn}I remember when you were born.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.04,1:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们不让我回家\N{\rEn}They wouldn't let me come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.79,1:18:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们说海军长官必须出席铺龙骨仪式\N{\rEn}The navy said an officer must be present for the laying of the keel, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.68,1:18:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但不必出席下水仪式\N{\rEn}not at the launching.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.79,1:18:06.30,注释,,0,0,0,,*船只的四大仪式\N铺龙骨KeelLaying 下水Launching 试航Commissioning 退役Decommisioning*
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.37,1:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我曾认为我父亲的付出是理所当然的\N{\rEn}I took my father for granted.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.09,1:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}一个和善的男人\N{\rEn}A sweet man.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.51,1:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我却认为他软弱\N{\rEn}I thought he was weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.43,1:18:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}一个焊接工 机械师\N{\rEn}A welder. Machinist.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.22,1:18:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他已经尽力了\N{\rEn}He did what he could.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.56,1:18:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他还推销房地产 保险\N{\rEn}Real estate. Insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.06,1:19:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他一天工作12个小时 一周工作6天\N{\rEn}He worked 12 hours a day, six days a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.24,1:19:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}四十年的辛勤工作 你知道他换来了什么吗\N{\rEn}Forty years he served them. You know what he got for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.91,1:19:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}一只腕表\N{\rEn}A wristwatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.79,1:19:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}有人开车碾过了他 任他倒在地上 自己跑了\N{\rEn}Somebody ran him over and left him in the street.
