Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.88,1:42:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他总能让别人与他为敌\N{\rEn}He turns people against him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.72,1:42:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他故意冒犯别人\N{\rEn}He offends them almost on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.89,1:42:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}尽管他为这个家真的做了很多\N{\rEn}He's a good provider though.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.85,1:42:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他勤奋工作\N{\rEn}He works hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.40,1:42:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我也可以去找份工作\N{\rEn}I could get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.28,1:42:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但他不想我这样\N{\rEn}He doesn't want me to though.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.61,1:42:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我考虑过了\N{\rEn}I've thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.62,1:42:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我现在还会速记打字\N{\rEn}I still know shorthand.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.71,1:42:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我在Benedict先生那里工作的时候\N{\rEn}When I worked at Benedict's.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.96,1:43:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我一分钟能打一百词\N{\rEn}I can type a hundred words a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.84,1:43:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}在这\N{\rEn}Right here!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.34,1:43:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那时我还没有结婚\N{\rEn}Before we got married.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.97,1:43:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不知道我现在还能做些什么\N{\rEn}I don't know what I could do now...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.35,1:43:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}有了这三个孩子后\N{\rEn}with three boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.77,1:43:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你以前很喜欢安静的\N{\rEn}You used to love science.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.44,1:43:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}喜欢结交自由自在的人\N{\rEn}Wanted to meet free people.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.53,1:43:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我曾经以为我永远不会结婚\N{\rEn}I thought I'd' never marry.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.71,1:43:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}也不会有人爱我\N{\rEn}And no one would love me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.84,1:43:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我错了\N{\rEn}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.59,1:43:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}当男孩们出生之后\N{\rEn}When those boys were born...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.64,1:43:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我的生活才真正开始\N{\rEn}my life began.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.65,1:44:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你要离开我们了吗\N{\rEn}Are you gonna leave us?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.73,1:44:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你为什么这么问\N{\rEn}Why do you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.32,1:44:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不知道\N{\rEn}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.16,1:44:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}没有为什么\N{\rEn}Just 'cause.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.26,1:44:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}啊\N{\rEn}- Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.01,1:44:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不\N{\rEn}- No!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.24,1:44:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我爱你啊\N{\rEn}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.07,1:44:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}抓住他\N{\rEn}Get him!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.66,1:44:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}抓住他\N{\rEn}- Get him!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.62,1:44:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}噢\N{\rEn}Oh-ho-ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.98,1:46:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你知道我把你当兄弟\N{\rEn}You know you're like a brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.52,1:46:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我就跟你直说了\N{\rEn}I want to be square with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.52,1:46:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你不能依赖你的朋友 但家人不一样\N{\rEn}You can't rely on your friends to, but family...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.62,1:46:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你强迫他们爱你 不管他们怎么想的\N{\rEn}You force them to love you whether they like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.12,1:46:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我忍你多久了 Ray\N{\rEn}How long I been putting up with you, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.62,1:46:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你来我家蹭吃蹭喝了多少年了\N{\rEn}How many years you been coming here, moochin' off my family?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.00,1:46:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你这么在意你姐姐 却一点忙都帮不上 \N{\rEn}Not lifting a hand to help out your sister you're so concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.05,1:46:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}嗯 我是你的仆人吗\N{\rEn}Hmm? Am I your servant?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.18,1:46:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我已经很体谅你的窘况了\N{\rEn}I have great sympathy for your nervous condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.26,1:46:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我理解你工作不易\N{\rEn}I understand how hard it is for you to keep at a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.18,1:46:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}妻子跑了 房车被烧毁了\N{\rEn}Wife ran off, your trailer burned down.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.94,1:46:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你可怜的妈妈还从灰烬里把锅碗瓢盆捡出来\N{\rEn}And your poor mother, pulling them pots and pans from the ashes,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.36,1:46:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}还想把它们擦亮\N{\rEn}trying to shine 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.07,1:46:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你以为你举起块大石头就能影响我的孩子们吗\N{\rEn}You think you can pick up a big rock and impress my boys?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.22,1:48:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你知道6为什么不开心吗\N{\rEn}Why was six upset?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.18,1:48:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}嗯？\N{\rEn}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.31,1:48:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}因为7吃了9\N{\rEn}'Cause seven ate nine.
