Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.18,1:49:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他出差了\N{\rEn}He's gone on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.74,1:49:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}哇哦\N{\rEn}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.49,1:49:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}哇哦\N{\rEn}- Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.23,1:50:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}抓住她 抓住她\N{\rEn}Get her! Get her!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.81,1:50:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}抓住她\N{\rEn}Get her!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.31,1:50:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}互相帮助\N{\rEn}- Help each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.90,1:50:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不要摔门\N{\rEn}Do not slam that screen door!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.94,1:50:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}等等\N{\rEn}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.90,1:50:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}爱所有人\N{\rEn}Love everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.49,1:50:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}爱每一片叶子\N{\rEn}Every leaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.04,1:50:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}爱每一缕光\N{\rEn}Every ray of light.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.26,1:50:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}宽恕\N{\rEn}Forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.78,1:51:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这是我的房子\N{\rEn}This is my house!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.79,1:51:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}是我让你们住 你们才能住在这\N{\rEn}You're allowed to live here!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.87,1:51:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}是我让你们住 你们才能住在这\N{\rEn}You're allowed to live here!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.50,1:51:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}别挡着我的道\N{\rEn}Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.42,1:51:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}闭嘴\N{\rEn}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.23,1:51:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我接到啦 接到啦\N{\rEn}I got it, I got it, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.45,1:53:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你有很多朋友吗\N{\rEn}Do you have a lot of friends?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.42,1:53:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我认识些朋友\N{\rEn}I know some guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.43,1:53:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你爸爸在哪\N{\rEn}Where's your daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.74,1:53:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你为什么不给我把树枝剪下来\N{\rEn}Why don't you cut me a switch.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.74,1:53:55.03,注释,,0,0,0,,*俗语 指成人让小孩子从树上剪树枝 以供他抽打使用*
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.42,1:54:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那样再好不过了吧\N{\rEn}Wouldn't that be nice?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.25,1:54:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}所有东西都由糖果做成 我们都能随心所欲\N{\rEn}Everything's made of candy, and we all get our way.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.97,1:54:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}每个人都 都像只青蛙一样蹦来蹦去\N{\rEn}And everybody's just — everybody's just hoppin' around like frogs.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.93,1:54:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}整个世界就像个青蛙池\N{\rEn}The whole world a frog pond.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.89,1:54:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你就在这屋子里和狗待着吧 你没有喂它水\N{\rEn}Grew up in this house with that dog. You didn't give him water.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.44,1:54:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}是什么让你的手没有长成鳍\N{\rEn}What stops your hands from turning into fins?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.12,1:54:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你琢磨琢磨吧\N{\rEn}Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.05,1:54:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}什么也没有\N{\rEn}Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.94,1:55:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}嗯？\N{\rEn}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.74,1:56:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}孩子们 把窗户关上\N{\rEn}- Boys, close the windows!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.31,1:57:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}主啊 这就是星期一的一场遭遇\N{\rEn}Lord, it was just a-ridin' on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.07,1:57:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}龙卷风袭来的一段经历\N{\rEn}Just a-ridin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.57,1:58:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}一些人有所得 一些人有所失\N{\rEn}A-gettin' some and a-missin' some.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.32,1:58:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}Bud只是其中之一\N{\rEn}And Bud was just one of the ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.49,1:58:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}一幢房子被卷起 横贯街道\N{\rEn}There was a house picked up, took across the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.12,1:58:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}然后又在风里穿行了一里路 里面的碗碟却整整齐齐\N{\rEn}Then picked up and took a mile down the road, and there wasn't a dish out of place.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.00,1:58:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这是怎么做到的\N{\rEn}How does it do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.46,1:58:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}雨倾泻而下 一位女士躲在门廊上\N{\rEn}Rain just pourin'. One lady hid on the porch.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.71,1:58:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他藏在车里\N{\rEn}He hid in his car.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.80,1:58:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}雨下得这么大 他什么都看不到\N{\rEn}Raining so hard, he couldn't even see.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.06,1:58:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}一辆车被撞毁 下一辆却完好无损\N{\rEn}One car smashed, the next car wouldn't have a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.73,1:58:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}真可怜\N{\rEn}Pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.94,1:58:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}市中心都毁了\N{\rEn}Downtown's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.86,1:58:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}114人死了\N{\rEn}114 dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.41,1:58:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}小心\N{\rEn}Look out!
