Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.32,2:00:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-小心 -小心\N{\rEn}- Watch out! - Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.12,2:00:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}跑\N{\rEn}Go!
