Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.54,2:01:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-嗯 这不是我们的 -谁在乎呢 你打算告密吗\N{\rEn}- Yeah, that's not ours. - Who cares? You gonna tell?
