Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.59,2:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}只有傻子才会被抓到\N{\rEn}Only stupid people get caught.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.64,2:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你觉得我很傻吗\N{\rEn}Think I'm stupid?
