Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.53,2:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}嘿 Steve\N{\rEn}Hey, Steve!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.54,2:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我认为他们不在家\N{\rEn}I don't think they're home.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.84,2:03:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}谁在乎呢\N{\rEn}Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.59,2:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这些是属于所有人的\N{\rEn}They belong to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.77,2:03:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不\N{\rEn}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.53,2:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来吧 我们来吧\N{\rEn}Come on. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.84,2:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们把它打碎吧\N{\rEn}I say let's bust it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.56,2:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}耶\N{\rEn}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.78,2:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-扔的不错 -耶\N{\rEn}- That's a good one. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.78,2:04:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}找到只青蛙\N{\rEn}- Found a frog.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.41,2:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-我们把它放在小火箭上发射出去吧 -它要跑了\N{\rEn}- Let's go set it off on a skyrocket. - He's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.04,2:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}后退 后退\N{\rEn}Get back! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:36.01,2:04:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}哇\N{\rEn}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.34,2:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}它到月亮上去了吗\N{\rEn}Did it go to the moon?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.06,2:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}它去哪了\N{\rEn}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.77,2:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}它在那儿呢\N{\rEn}Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.14,2:04:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这只是个实验\N{\rEn}It was an experiment!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:56.36,2:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}骗子\N{\rEn}Liar.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.07,2:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}再别做这种事了\N{\rEn}Never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.74,2:05:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}能答应我吗\N{\rEn}Promise?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.62,2:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你准备告诉爸爸吗\N{\rEn}You gonna tell Dad?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.08,2:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}大人们只是在吓唬你\N{\rEn}They're just trying to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.92,2:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}让你保持无知\N{\rEn}Keep you ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.59,2:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你要知道\N{\rEn}Things you got to learn.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.60,2:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}在我们看到事物之前怎么可能认识它呢\N{\rEn}How can we know stuff till we look?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.29,2:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们不让你做的事\N{\rEn}They say you can't try stuff?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.41,2:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们自己却做\N{\rEn}They do.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.92,2:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你还怕什么\N{\rEn}What do you need to be afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.38,2:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你在害怕\N{\rEn}You afraid.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.59,2:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我看出来了\N{\rEn}I see it.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.80,2:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}在这儿 在这儿\N{\rEn}Right here! Right here!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.25,2:12:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不能跟你说\N{\rEn}I can't talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.51,2:12:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你别看着我\N{\rEn}Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:10.73,2:13:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我怎么了\N{\rEn}What have I started?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.40,2:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我都做了什么\N{\rEn}What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:02.32,2:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}把它插到这\N{\rEn}Stick it in there.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:43.28,2:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我相信你\N{\rEn}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.74,2:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}砰\N{\rEn}Buzz!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.71,2:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你累了 -才没有\N{\rEn}- You tired? - No.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.92,2:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我从来不会累\N{\rEn}I never get tired.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.38,2:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你今早就很累啊 -不 那是我装的\N{\rEn}- Did this morning. - No, I was just pretending.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.76,2:15:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你说我是骗子吗 -不\N{\rEn}- Gonna call me a liar? - No.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.22,2:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不想打架\N{\rEn}I don't want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.27,2:15:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}害怕了\N{\rEn}Afraid to?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:15.52,2:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不 我就是不想\N{\rEn}No, I just don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:18.98,2:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}如果我说你害怕了 你会叫我骗子吗\N{\rEn}If I was to say you're scared, would you call me a liar?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.98,2:15:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不会\N{\rEn}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.15,2:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那你就是害怕了 对吧\N{\rEn}Then you're scared, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:35.41,2:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}哈哈\N{\rEn}Ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:37.54,2:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}别闹了\N{\rEn}Quit it.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.87,2:16:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}能原谅我吗\N{\rEn}Forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:56.75,2:16:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你最好收回你的话\N{\rEn}Take it back!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:04.29,2:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你干什么呢\N{\rEn}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:10.09,2:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}回答我\N{\rEn}Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:22.60,2:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}下一个词是propel\N{\rEn}Next word is “propel.”
Dialogue: 0,2:17:28.82,2:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这些词我们周二刚复习过 我很高兴看到大部分同学都写对了\N{\rEn}These are words we went over Tuesday, so I'm happy to see most of you getting them right.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.55,2:17:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你的能力不止于此\N{\rEn}You can do better than what you've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:59.98,2:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你能告诉我关于木星的一些知识点吗\N{\rEn}Can you tell me something about Jupiter?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:09.86,2:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你看上去在害怕什么\N{\rEn}You seem afraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:19.95,2:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他甚至无法画完一幅画\N{\rEn}He wouldn't even complete his painting.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:23.46,2:18:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他害怕会画错\N{\rEn}He was afraid it might be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:30.88,2:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我跟他说这没什么对错\N{\rEn}I told him it can't be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:33.51,2:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他是个好男孩\N{\rEn}He's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.01,2:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他就是看上去缺乏自信\N{\rEn}He just seems to lack confidence.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.06,2:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他并没有专心听我的课\N{\rEn}He doesn't seem to hear my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:46.98,2:18:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}愣神\N{\rEn}Stares.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.11,2:18:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}比如那篇关于埃及的报告 他是从世界百科全书上照抄的\N{\rEn}Like on his Egypt report, he copped it right out of the World Book.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:56.32,2:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-他抄袭了 -是的\N{\rEn}- He cheated? - He cheated.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:58.62,2:19:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他破坏课堂秩序\N{\rEn}He disrupts the entire class.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:00.91,2:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他掌握不了评论文章的写法\N{\rEn}He cannot handle criticism.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:02.66,2:19:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们一直在引导他\N{\rEn}We're constantly getting on him all the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:04.62,2:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我把一切都给了你\N{\rEn}I give you everything I got!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:06.75,2:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}在我小时候还在南奥斯汀时\N{\rEn}When I was growing up in South Austin,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:08.84,2:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我爸爸希望我能把所有事都做得尽善尽美\N{\rEn}my dad wanted everything perfect.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.00,2:19:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}如果我做得有瑕疵 他就会打我的屁股\N{\rEn}If I didn't do it perfect, he'd wear my little butt out.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.34,2:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这些年来 我对我的运动员们也经常这样要求\N{\rEn}And I pretty much done that over the years with my athletes.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:16.80,2:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但对学生就没必要这样\N{\rEn}Not necessarily the students.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:18.39,2:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但对屁股挨板子的恐惧可能会有奇妙的作用\N{\rEn}But that fear of that board on their little butt can do wonders.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:21.56,2:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}最令我惊讶的是 当我告诉他我要找家长开会时\N{\rEn}What really surprised me, when I told him I was gonna have this conference with you,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:25.81,2:19:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他脸一下子红了\N{\rEn}he went totally pink.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.27,2:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我总是在做蠢事\N{\rEn}I always do stupid things.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:31.65,2:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我想回到小时候多好啊\N{\rEn}I want to be little again.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:49.67,2:19:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}“Coecha makeecha” 那个词语\N{\rEn}“Coecha makeecha.” The words.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:53.96,2:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}什么词语\N{\rEn}What words?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.47,2:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那个让人们不再刻薄的词语\N{\rEn}The words that'll stop people from being mean.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.97,2:20:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我再也听不到它了\N{\rEn}I'll never find it again.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.10,2:20:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}听啊\N{\rEn}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.52,2:20:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我再也不信这种事情了\N{\rEn}I don't believe in that stuff anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.33,2:20:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}过来\N{\rEn}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.54,2:20:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不\N{\rEn}No!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:35.34,2:20:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不会做你让我做的任何事的\N{\rEn}I'm not gonna do everything you tell me to.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:39.47,2:20:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我想做什么就做什么\N{\rEn}I'm gonna do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.89,2:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你知道什么呢 你就这样让他骑在你头上\N{\rEn}What do you know? You let him run all over you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:38.24,2:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我怎么才能回到过去\N{\rEn}How do I get back...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:45.53,2:21:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们在哪\N{\rEn}where they are?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.77,2:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-儿子你好吗 -挺好\N{\rEn}- How are you, Son? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:22.36,2:22:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这个挺重的 你得两只手拎着\N{\rEn}This one's heavy. You're gonna need two hands for that one.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:32.04,2:22:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}看看这个\N{\rEn}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.83,2:22:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}注意啦 你知道这个是什么吗\N{\rEn}Careful now. You know what that — You know what —
Dialogue: 0,2:22:37.34,2:22:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-中文吗 -对啦 是中文\N{\rEn}- Chinese? - That's Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:39.05,2:22:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}很不错嘛 是中文\N{\rEn}That's very good. Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.67,2:22:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你父亲我环游世界 一路到了中国\N{\rEn}Your father went all around the world, all the way to China.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:45.80,2:22:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那是泛美航空 你父亲我坐的航班\N{\rEn}That's Pan Am airlines. That's what your father flew on.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:49.31,2:22:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}整个卫生间都是不锈钢做的 连洗手池都是\N{\rEn}The entire bathrooms are stainless steel, even the washbasin.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:52.89,2:22:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我相信这笔生意进展的不错\N{\rEn}I feel confident the deal's going through.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:55.94,2:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}如果他们要放弃这笔生意 让他们去死好了\N{\rEn}If not, they can forget it. I'll tell them all to go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:59.27,2:23:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-那是从德国带回来的 -这个怎么用啊\N{\rEn}- That's from Germany. - How do you use them?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:01.28,2:23:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}看到了吗\N{\rEn}See that?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:05.57,2:23:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}儿子 把那个放下来\N{\rEn}Put that down, Son.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:07.70,2:23:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}能让Gayler过来玩吗\N{\rEn}Can Gayler come over?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:10.16,2:23:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}有你的家人陪你还不够吗\N{\rEn}Is your family not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:43.82,2:23:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你知道我在你出生时做了什么吗\N{\rEn}You know what I did when you were born?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:46.49,2:23:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我跑出去在草坪上手舞足蹈\N{\rEn}I went out and I danced on the lawn.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:49.87,2:23:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}兴奋地掏出我的配枪射击\N{\rEn}Shot off my service revolver.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:54.87,2:23:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你看看你现在 望着窗户愣神 浪费时间\N{\rEn}See you wasting your time staring out the window.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:58.67,2:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那能让你得到什么\N{\rEn}Where's that gonna get you?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.88,2:24:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我为你牺牲了很多\N{\rEn}I make sacrifices for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:04.84,2:24:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}请用你的所作所为来珍惜我的付出\N{\rEn}Honor those sacrifices by what you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:08.93,2:24:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你刚才说啥 -“抱歉 你刚才说了什么”\N{\rEn}- What? - Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.81,2:24:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}“抱歉 你刚才说了什么 先生”\N{\rEn}Excuse me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:14.35,2:24:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这么说 “抱歉 你刚才说了什么”\N{\rEn}Say it. “Excuse me.”
Dialogue: 0,2:24:16.31,2:24:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}抱歉 你刚才说了什么\N{\rEn}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:17.89,2:24:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-“先生” -先生\N{\rEn}- “Sir.” - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:20.61,2:24:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}好好听着 儿子 你应该学些东西\N{\rEn}Just listen, Son. You might actually learn something.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:29.03,2:24:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-弟弟在哪呢 -这不是你现在应该关心的\N{\rEn}- Where's my brother? - That's not important right now, is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:34.83,2:24:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}好吧\N{\rEn}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:36.08,2:24:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你看看这个\N{\rEn}You see this?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.83,2:24:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你知道我为什么留着它吗\N{\rEn}You know why I keep that?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.88,2:24:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这是我自己公司的公章\N{\rEn}It's the official seal of my own company.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:46.05,2:24:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我自己创办的公司\N{\rEn}The one I formed.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:48.80,2:24:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}直到我在中国喝了未杀菌的啤酒后得了肝炎\N{\rEn}Till I got hepatitis from drinking unpasteurized beer in China.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:58.64,2:25:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}把那根棍子放下 儿子\N{\rEn}Put the stick down, Son.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.41,2:25:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我尽我所能保护你\N{\rEn}I protected you as best I can,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:16.79,2:25:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但我没有机会接受教育\N{\rEn}but I didn't get an education.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:19.16,2:25:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}而你有\N{\rEn}You will.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:23.34,2:25:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但我可以补偿自己\N{\rEn}But I can redeem myself.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:30.09,2:25:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你就是我的自由\N{\rEn}You're my freedom.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:59.00,2:26:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这就是你跟我说的吗\N{\rEn}Is that what you're telling me?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:01.12,2:26:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}好吧 也许你应该在广告里说的直接一些\N{\rEn}Well, maybe you ought to get your ad straight.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:03.21,2:26:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你想想吧 孩子们\N{\rEn}You think? Boys!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:05.92,2:26:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你没必要这么生气 你..\N{\rEn}You don't have to leave in a huff. You can —
Dialogue: 0,2:26:09.13,2:26:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-你刚才说什么呢 孩子们我们走了 -我说你没必要这么生气\N{\rEn}- Did you say something? Boys, let's go. - You don't have to leave in a huff.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:12.01,2:26:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我告你吧 如果我有世界上所有的钱..\N{\rEn}I tell you what. If I had all the money in the world —
Dialogue: 0,2:26:14.05,2:26:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你这样的骗人精我见多了\N{\rEn}I've heard about enough from clip artists like you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:21.06,2:26:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}放松点\N{\rEn}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.56,2:26:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}什么\N{\rEn}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:35.03,2:26:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}希望不要像上次等那么久\N{\rEn}Hope it's not going to take as long as last time.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:38.29,2:26:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}做的筋道点\N{\rEn}Al dente.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:43.42,2:26:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这是主观观点 你知道有什么区别吗\N{\rEn}Subjective point of view. You know the difference?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:45.71,2:26:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}主观意味着是你自己的见解 不能被他人证明\N{\rEn}Subjective means it comes from your mind. Can't be proven by other people.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:48.71,2:26:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}嗯\N{\rEn}- Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:51.13,2:26:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}唔\N{\rEn}Oop.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:57.01,2:26:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-很高兴又见到你 -嗯\N{\rEn}- Good to see you again. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:59.68,2:27:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们走吧 孩子们\N{\rEn}Let's go, boys.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.64,2:27:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}快点\N{\rEn}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.73,2:27:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你在害怕吗 再游远点\N{\rEn}You afraid? Go out further.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:13.19,2:27:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那是噬鱼蛇吗\N{\rEn}Is that a water moccasin?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:16.66,2:27:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你只看到了脑袋吗\N{\rEn}You see a head, and that's all?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:18.91,2:27:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}那是海龟\N{\rEn}That's a turtle.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:38.55,2:27:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}有些事情你做不到 我也同样如此\N{\rEn}There are things you can't do. Well, there are things I can't do either.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:44.14,2:27:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你别叫我爸爸 叫我父亲\N{\rEn}You are not to call me Dad. You will call me Father.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:46.81,2:27:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-但.. -别打断我\N{\rEn}- But — - Don't interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:48.06,2:27:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}-但你自己.. -别打岔\N{\rEn}- But you did. - Don't interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:56.03,2:28:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}这是你的家 你随时可以让我滚\N{\rEn}It's your house. You can kick me out whenever you want to.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:05.46,2:28:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你想要杀了我\N{\rEn}You'd like to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:32.48,2:28:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他为什么会出生\N{\rEn}Why was he born?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:59.78,2:30:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}求你了 上帝 杀了他\N{\rEn}Please, God, kill him.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:06.53,2:30:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}让他去死\N{\rEn}Let him die.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:13.33,2:30:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}让他远离我的生活\N{\rEn}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:36.73,2:30:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}她只爱我一个\N{\rEn}She only loves me!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:50.08,2:30:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}主啊 求你保佑你的孩子 赐予他恩典\N{\rEn}Defend, O Lord, this, thy child, with thy heavenly grace,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:54.29,2:30:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}保佑他永受圣恩\N{\rEn}that he may continue thine forever...
Dialogue: 0,2:30:57.59,2:31:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}日渐成长 圣灵赐福\N{\rEn}and daily increase in thy holy spirit more and more
Dialogue: 0,2:31:01.88,2:31:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}直至他来到你永恒的王国\N{\rEn}until he come unto thy everlasting kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:05.47,2:31:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}阿门\N{\rEn}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:47.76,2:31:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}看我的\N{\rEn}See somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:40.36,2:32:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}把你手指放过来\N{\rEn}Put your finger over it.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:44.23,2:32:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}像这样\N{\rEn}Like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:47.53,2:32:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}来吧\N{\rEn}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:46.59,2:33:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我无法做我想做的\N{\rEn}What I want to do I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:54.60,2:33:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我做的都是我讨厌的\N{\rEn}I do what I hate.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:55.95,2:34:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}给你\N{\rEn}Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:58.03,2:35:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你想的话就打我吧\N{\rEn}You can hit me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:17.76,2:35:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}对不起\N{\rEn}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:22.93,2:35:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你是我的弟弟\N{\rEn}You're my brother.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:08.69,2:36:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你想向我呈现什么\N{\rEn}What is it you showed me?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:19.99,2:36:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我不知该怎么称呼\N{\rEn}I didn't know how to name you then...
Dialogue: 0,2:36:27.42,2:36:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但我知道那是你\N{\rEn}but I see it was you.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:35.26,2:36:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你总是在呼唤我\N{\rEn}Always you were calling me.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:45.10,2:36:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你的妈妈和我都没有机会读完大学\N{\rEn}We never got to finish college, your mother and I.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:49.85,2:36:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}让你有更好的教育机会对我们很重要\N{\rEn}But it's important to us that we get you the best education
Dialogue: 0,2:36:53.57,2:36:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们可以给你提供这个机会\N{\rEn}we can possibly provide.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:00.82,2:37:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}所以我们决定 为了你好\N{\rEn}So we've decided that it's in your best interest
Dialogue: 0,2:37:03.91,2:37:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们要把你送去学校\N{\rEn}that we send you away to school.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:08.12,2:37:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}只有100英里远\N{\rEn}Now, it's only a hundred miles away.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:09.96,2:37:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们周末和假期还是能去看你\N{\rEn}We'll still be able to see you on weekends and vacations.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:17.13,2:37:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我跟那里的人说过了 他们都知道你是个好男孩了\N{\rEn}I've talked to the people there. They know you're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:39.53,2:37:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我想这会是最好的选择\N{\rEn}I think this will be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:43.95,2:37:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}既然你难以和你的父亲\N{\rEn}You've been having such trouble with your father.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:48.79,2:37:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你的同学相处\N{\rEn}And with your classmates at school.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:54.50,2:37:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们没能尽到家长的责任\N{\rEn}We haven't been good parents,
Dialogue: 0,2:37:59.26,2:38:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}不然不会给你造成这么大的压力\N{\rEn}or you wouldn't be under all this tension.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:09.85,2:38:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我们应该做个更好的榜样\N{\rEn}We should have set a better example.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:26.99,2:38:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我会很想你的\N{\rEn}I will miss you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:29.74,2:40:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我希望有人爱我 因为我很棒\N{\rEn}I wanted to be loved because I was great.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:35.58,2:40:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}是个顶天立地的男儿\N{\rEn}A big man.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:40.13,2:40:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}但我什么都不是\N{\rEn}I'm nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:45.67,2:40:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}看看我们身边的美好\N{\rEn}Look at the glory around us.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:51.80,2:40:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}树木与鸟儿\N{\rEn}Trees and birds.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:57.64,2:40:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我活在羞愧中\N{\rEn}I lived in shame.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:02.98,2:41:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我没有珍惜这一切 忽视了身边的美好\N{\rEn}I dishonored it all and didn't notice the glory.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:12.37,2:41:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我是个愚蠢的人\N{\rEn}I'm a foolish man.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:19.33,2:41:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们要关闭工厂\N{\rEn}They're closing the plant.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:25.21,2:41:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}他们让我选择\N{\rEn}They gave me a choice.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:30.01,2:41:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}要么失业\N{\rEn}No job...
Dialogue: 0,2:41:34.64,2:41:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}要么换个没人乐意做的岗位\N{\rEn}or transfer to a job nobody wants.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:47.19,2:41:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}父亲\N{\rEn}Father.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:51.24,2:41:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我从来没有懈怠过一天的工作\N{\rEn}I never missed a day of work.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:53.95,2:41:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}母亲\N{\rEn}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:56.62,2:41:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我每个星期日都去捐税\N{\rEn}I tithed every Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:56.62,2:41:58.62,注释,,0,0,0,,*特指缴纳给教会的捐款*
Dialogue: 0,2:42:02.58,2:42:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你们永远是我心中的羁绊\N{\rEn}Always you wrestle inside me.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:10.42,2:42:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}永远都是\N{\rEn}Always you will.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:14.14,2:42:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你知道吗 Jack 我想让你做的\N{\rEn}You know, Jack, all I ever wanted for you was...
Dialogue: 0,2:42:18.64,2:42:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}无非是想让你变得强大\N{\rEn}to make you strong and...
Dialogue: 0,2:42:21.73,2:42:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}能够掌握自己命运\N{\rEn}grow up and be your own boss.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:27.11,2:42:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}也许我对你过于苛责了\N{\rEn}Maybe I've been tough on you.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:31.53,2:42:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我并不为此感到自豪\N{\rEn}I'm not proud of that.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:35.28,2:42:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我和你一样糟糕\N{\rEn}I'm as bad as you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:40.50,2:42:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}相比于妈妈 我更像你\N{\rEn}I'm more like you than her.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:51.13,2:42:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你们仨是我人生唯一的成就 除此之外我一无所有\N{\rEn}You boys are about all I've done in life. Otherwise I've drawn a zilch.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:03.19,2:43:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你是我的一切 我想要的一切\N{\rEn}You're all I have. You're all I wanna have.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:13.74,2:43:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我亲爱的儿子\N{\rEn}My sweet boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:22.37,2:45:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你就打算在那像个木头一样站着么\N{\rEn}You just gonna stand there like a bump on a log?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:29.33,2:45:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}放里面\N{\rEn}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:46.26,2:47:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}幸福的唯一方式就是去爱\N{\rEn}The only way to be happy is to love.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:05.95,2:48:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}只有去爱\N{\rEn}Unless you love...
Dialogue: 0,2:48:09.66,2:48:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}你的生命才不会一晃而过\N{\rEn}your life will flash by.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:23.05,2:48:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}请善待他们\N{\rEn}Do good to them.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:29.93,2:48:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}奇迹\N{\rEn}Wonder.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:36.06,2:48:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}希望\N{\rEn}Hope.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:06.40,2:50:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}弟弟\N{\rEn}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:58.37,2:50:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}养育我们\N{\rEn}Keep us.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:08.34,2:51:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}指引我们\N{\rEn}Guide us...
Dialogue: 0,2:51:19.68,2:51:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}直到时间的尽头\N{\rEn}till the end of time.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:54.34,2:51:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}跟着我\N{\rEn}Follow me.
