Dialogue: 0,2:59:31.63,2:59:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}♪阿门♪\N{\rEn}♪ Amen ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:59:42.81,2:59:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}♪阿门♪\N{\rEn}♪ Amen ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:59:50.44,2:59:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\rzh}我把儿子交付给你\N{\rEn}I give you my son.
